    \n                \n                \n                \n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </li>   \n        <li class=\"title\">\n\n            <a class=\"a\" href=\"../../tzgg.htm\" title=\"通知公告\"><h3>通知公告</h3></a><i></i>\n        </li>   \n    </ul>\n</nav>\n<section class=\"nav_mask\"></section>\n\n<!--============================头部 结束=============================-->\n\n\n<!--============================主体 开始=============================-->\n\n<section id=\"banner\" class=\"banner\">\n     <ul class=\"slow_miso miso-initialized miso-slider\">\n        <div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"miso-list draggable\"><div class=\"miso-track\" role=\"listbox\" style=\"opacity: 1; width: 1280px; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);\"><li class=\"miso-slide miso-current miso-active\" data-miso-index=\"0\" aria-hidden=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"option\" aria-describedby=\"miso-slide00\" style=\"width: 1280px;\">\n <a tabindex=\"0\">\n            <img src=\"../../images/banner/ban7ner.jpg\" alt=\"\"> </a>\n        </li></div></div>\n    </ul> \n\n</section>\n<script>\n$(\".banner ul\").miso({\n    dots:true\n});\n</script>\n\n<section class=\"miso_content\">\n\n<section class=\"n_container n_lvli_detail\">\n    <div class=\"w1200\">\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"bg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"content_li\">\n                <div class=\"title001\">\n                    <h3>\n\n\n\n研究系列</h3>\n                </div>\n \n             \n                <div class=\"fl00 fl01 clearfix\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format4.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"left fl\">\n                        <div class=\"img slow fl\">\n                                                    <img src=\"/__local/F/F5/41/3335D9F0C5E8ABB56B4892A4EA6_79718AAD_511D.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: #39b54a 3px solid;\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"con fr\">\n                            <h3>张明徽</h3>\n                            <dl><dd>清华大学基础医学院，副教授</dd>\n                            \n                            </dl>                            \n                            <p>\n                                <b>Contact Us：</b><br>\n                              \n                                E-mail:  mh-zhang@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn<br>\n                                Address：中国北京市海淀区清华大学医学科学楼B343\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"right fr\">\n \n       \n\n       \n\n\n\n\n<div id=\"vsb_content_4\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<div>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">教育背景</h4>\n <p>1989-1994 潍坊医学院临床医学 学士</p>\n <p>1994-1997 第二军医大学免疫学研究所 硕士</p>\n <p>1999-2002 第二军医大学免疫学研究所 博士</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">工作经历</h4>\n <p>1997-1999 第二军医大学免疫学教研室 助教</p>\n <p>1999-2004 第二军医大学免疫学研究所 讲师</p>\n <p>2004-2005 清华大学医学院 博士后</p>\n <p>2005-2024 清华大学医学院 副教授 2024-至今 清华大学基础医学院 副教授</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">研究领域</h4>\n <p>肿瘤免疫学。本实验室主要围绕细胞免疫学的基础研究及肿瘤的免疫学治疗方法开展研究。免疫微环境可以转变免疫细胞的功能状态，让激活性树突状细胞转化为抑制性树突状细胞，这是免疫应答平息的主动调节机制，并进一步通过研究抑制性树突状细胞探索其对自身免疫性疾病治疗的潜在意义。自2005年主要研究方向集中在CD8<sup>+</sup>NKT的生物学功能研究和应用研究。CD8<sup>+</sup>NKT细胞是具有抗原特异性和非特异性双重抗肿瘤作用的细胞亚群，通过开展多项临床研究，探索其在肺癌、肝癌、黑色素瘤等多种实体肿瘤的治疗作用。</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">科学贡献</h4>\n <p>发现了成熟树突状细胞可以在免疫微环境中增殖再分化；在国际上率先建立了NKT的大规模扩增方法，发现了NKT的双向抗肿瘤效应。创立了基于NKT的新一代抗肿瘤免疫细胞治疗技术，该研究是“十二五重大新药创制计划”支持的唯一细胞治疗项目，并获得美国专利授权。目前在北京大学肿瘤医院、长海医院、东方肝胆医院、江苏大学附属医院、齐鲁大学南山分院开展临床研究，累积案例近700例，用于治疗肺癌、肝癌、黑色素瘤等多种实体肿瘤。以第一作者和通讯作者在Nature Immunology、Blood、Scientific Reports等免疫学高水平杂志发表文章；主持、参加多项自然科学基金、十二五国家新药创制计划、重大传染病计划以及“863”计划等国家项目。</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">荣誉奖励</h4>\n <p>2020 人民网“年度科普达人”和“年度科普红人”</p>\n <p>2018《健康报》“年度最受医生欢迎文章”奖</p>\n <p>2009 清华大学第八届良师益友</p>\n <p>2006 中华医学科技奖一等奖</p>\n <p>2006上海市医学科技奖 一等奖</p>\n <p>2005 全国优秀博士学位论文（第一完成人）</p>\n <p>2004 中国高等院校10大科技进展</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">代表性论文及专利</h4>\n <p>1.Wang, Q., S. Chen, Z.Guo, S. Xia and M. Zhang*.(2024) NK-like CD8 T cell: one potential evolutionary continuum between adaptive memory and innate immunity. Clin Exp Immunol, 217(2):136-150.</p>\n <p>2.Yu, W., X. Yuan, F. Ye, C. Mao, J. Li, M. Zhang, D.Chen and S. Xia. (2022). <a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/36169194/\">Role of allogeneic natural killer T cells in the treatment of a patient with gefitinib-sensitive lung adenocarcinoma.</a> Immunotherapy, 14(16):1291-1296.</p>\n <p>3.Yu, W., F. Ye, X. Yuan, Y. Ma, C. Mao, X. Li , J. Li, C. Dai, F. Qian, J. Li, X. Fan, Y. Zhou, D. Wang, Z. Guo, H. An, M. Zhang, D. Chen and S. Xia.<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/34332557/\">A (2021) phase I/II clinical trial on the efficacy and safety of NKT cells combined with gefitinib for advanced EGFR-mutated non-small-cell lung cancer.</a> BMC Cancer, 21(1):877.</p>\n <p>4.Li, Z., Y. Wu, C. Wang and M. Zhang*. (2019). \"Mouse CD8(+)NKT-like cells exert dual cytotoxicity against mouse tumor cells and myeloid-derived suppressor cells.\" Cancer Immunol Immunother 68(8): 1303-1315.</p>\n <p>5.Wang, C., Z. Li, Z. Zhu, Y. Chai, Y. Wu, Z. Yuan, Z. Chang, Z. Wang and M. Zhang *.(2019). Allogeneic dendritic cells induce potent antitumor immunity by activating KLRG1(+)CD8 T cells. Sci Rep 9(1): 15527.</p>\n <p>6.Ma, H., Chen, S., He, Y., Huang, J., Xu, Y., Wang, C., Lei, C., Lu, T., Xiao, S., Mao, J., Xu, Y., Guo, H., Li, B., M. Zhang and He, X*. (2018). Redirecting T cells to glypican-3 with 28.41BB.ζ and 28.ζ-41BBL CARs for hepatocellular carcinoma treatment. Protein &amp; cell, 9(7), 664–669.</p>\n <p>7.M. Zhang*.（2018）. Adoptive cell transfer therapy: A strategic rethinking of combination cancer therapy. Science SUPPLEMENT. Precision medicine and cancer immunology in China.52-56.</p>\n <p>8.Zhao, L., Yang, G., Bai, H., M. Zhang and Mou, D. (2017). NCTD promotes Birinapant-mediated anticancer activity in breast cancer cells by downregulation of c-FLIP. Oncotarget, 8(16), 26886–26895.</p>\n <p>9.Chen, D., Y. Wang, H. Wang, Y. Wu, S. Xia and M. Zhang*. (2015). \"CD8(+) T activation attenuates CD4(+) T proliferation through dendritic cells modification.\" Cell Immunol 296(2): 138-148.</p>\n <p>10.Wang, C., X. Liu, Z. Li, Y. Chai, Y. Jiang, Q. Wang, Y. Ji, Z. Zhu, Y. Wan, Z. Yuan, Z. Chang and M. Zhang *.(2015). \"CD8(+)NKT-like cells regulate the immune response by killing antigen-bearing DCs.\" Sci Rep 5: 14124.</p>\n <p>11.Xia, S*., X. Li, L. Cheng, M. Han, X. Liu, H. Xu, M. Zhang , Q. Shao and L. Qi (2014). \"Chronic intake of high fish oil diet induces myeloid-derived suppressor cells to promote tumor growth.\" Cancer Immunol Immunother 63(7): 663-673.</p>\n <p>12.Chen, Z., Y. Han, Y. Gu, Y. Liu, Z. Jiang, M. Zhang and X. Cao* (2013). \"CD11c(high)CD8+ regulatory T cell feedback inhibits CD4 T cell immune response via Fas ligand-Fas pathway.\" J Immunol 190(12): 6145-6154.</p>\n <p>13.Zhong, K., W. Song, Q. Wang, C. Wang, X. Liu, D. Chen, Z. Zhu, Y. Wu, W. Zhang* and M. Zhang *.(2012). \"Murine myeloid dendritic cells that phagocytose apoptotic T cells inhibit the immune response via NO.\" PLoS One 7(11): e49378.</p>\n <p>14.Jia, D., W. Rao, C. Wang, C. Jin, S. Wang, D. Chen, M. Zhang , J. Guo, Z. Chang and J. Liu* (2011). \"Inhibition of B16 murine melanoma metastasis and enhancement of immunity by fever-range whole body hyperthermia.\" Int J Hyperthermia 27(3): 275-285.</p>\n <p>15.Bai, B., Song, W., Ji, Y., Liu, X., Tian, L., Wang, C., Chen, D., Zhang, X and M. Zhang *.(2009). Microglia and microglia-like cell differentiated from DC inhibit CD4 T cell proliferation. PloS one, 4(11), e7869.</p>\n <p>16.Tang, H., Z. Guo, M. Zhang, J. Wang, G. Chen and X. Cao *(2006). \"Endothelial stroma programs hematopoietic stem cells to differentiate into regulatory dendritic cells through IL-10.\" Blood 108(4): 1189-1197.</p>\n <p>17.An, H., H. Xu, M. Zhang, J. Zhou, T. Feng, C. Qian, R. Qi and X. Cao* (2005). \"Src homology 2 domain-containing inositol-5-phosphatase 1 (SHIP1) negatively regulates TLR4-mediated LPS response primarily through a phosphatase activity- and PI-3K-independent mechanism.\" Blood 105(12): 4685-4692.</p>\n <p>18.Guo, J., M. Zhang, B. Wang, Z. Yuan, Z. Guo, T. Chen, Y. Yu, Z. Qin and X. Cao* (2003). \"Fractalkine transgene induces T-cell-dependent antitumor immunity through chemoattraction and activation of dendritic cells.\" Int J Cancer 103(2): 212-220.</p>\n <p>19.Guo, Z., M. Zhang, H. An, W. Chen, S. Liu, J. Guo, Y. Yu and X. Cao *(2003). \"Fas ligation induces IL-1beta-dependent maturation and IL-1beta-independent survival of dendritic cells: different roles of ERK and NF-kappaB signaling pathways.\" Blood 102(13): 4441-4447.</p>\n <p>20.Guo, Z., M. Zhang , H. Tang and X. Cao* (2005). \"Fas signal links innate and adaptive immunity by promoting dendritic-cell secretion of CC and CXC chemokines.\" Blood 106(6): 2033-2041.</p>\n <p>21.Han, Y., M. Zhang, N. Li, T. Chen, Y. Zhang, T. Wan and X. Cao* (2004). \"KLRL1, a novel killer cell lectinlike receptor, inhibits natural killer cell cytotoxicity.\" Blood 104(9): 2858-2866.</p>\n <p>22.Pan, J., M. Zhang, J. Wang, Q. Wang, D. Xia, W. Sun, L. Zhang, H. Yu and X. Cao* (2005). \"Intratumoral injection of interferon-gamma gene-modified dendritic cells elicits potent antitumor effects: effective induction of tumor-specific CD8+ CTL response.\" J Cancer Res Clin Oncol 131(7): 468-478.</p>\n <p>23.M. Zhang,H. Tang, Z. Guo, H. An, X. Zhu, W. Song, J. Guo, X. Huang, T. Chen, J. Wang and X. Cao* (2004). \"Splenic stroma drives mature dend